      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The chassis remains factory-spec with zero torsional fatigue; the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the Vanos system and rod bearings have been serviced to ensure peak mechanical longevity. Suspension geometry is tight, utilizing original Sachs dampers and bushings for authentic feedback. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the paint depth and interior bolster integrity are flawless. A mechanically transparent, turn-key investment for the discerning driver.",
